quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  23,90,"Bal ataynahum bilhaqqiwa-innahum lakathiboon"
  23,91,"Ma ittakhatha Allahumin waladin wama kana maAAahu min ilahin ithanlathahaba kullu ilahin bima khalaqa walaAAalabaAAduhum AAala baAAdin subhana AllahiAAamma yasifoon"
  23,92,"AAalimi alghaybi washshahadatifataAAala AAamma yushrikoon"
  23,93,"Qul rabbi imma turiyannee mayooAAadoon"
  23,94,"Rabbi fala tajAAalnee fee alqawmi aththalimeen"
  23,95,"Wa-inna AAala an nuriyaka manaAAiduhum laqadiroon"
  23,96,"IdfaAA billatee hiya ahsanu assayyi-atanahnu aAAlamu bima yasifoon"
  23,97,"Waqul rabbi aAAoothu bika min hamazatiashshayateen"
  23,98,"WaaAAoothu bika rabbi an yahduroon"
  23,99,"Hatta itha jaa ahadahumualmawtu qala rabbi irjiAAoon"
  23,100,"LaAAallee aAAmalu salihanfeema taraktu kalla innaha kalimatun huwa qa-iluhawamin wara-ihim barzakhun ila yawmi yubAAathoon"
  23,101,"Fa-itha nufikha fee assoorifala ansaba baynahum yawma-ithin walayatasaaloon"
  23,102,"Faman thaqulat mawazeenuhu faola-ikahumu almuflihoon"
  23,103,"Waman khaffat mawazeenuhu faola-ikaallatheena khasiroo anfusahum fee jahannama khalidoon"
  23,104,"Talfahu wujoohahumu annaruwahum feeha kalihoon"
